{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775810799486,"sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","part":{"id":"prt_d7692677b001qwj2Z9blLdzMQv","messageID":"msg_d769261560011IBw74KrOV3kpe","sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775810828467,"sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","part":{"id":"prt_d769269ee001LvJIkHxRH6nb7R","messageID":"msg_d769261560011IBw74KrOV3kpe","sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_13b7d3e83a9c4203a46afcaf","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n## 概述\n从 AR-001（AgentRuntime）和 AR-002（CodeInterpreter）中提取并规范化共享类型与常量，建立 `pkg/apis` 模块中跨 CRD 复用的类型基座。\n\n## 元信息\n- **Module**: pkg/apis\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n\n## 目的\nAgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 两个 CRD 共享 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType` 等类型定义。本变更将这些共享类型与常量从具体 CRD 类型文件中解耦，形成独立的共享类型模块，确保单一数据源、避免重复定义，并为后续新增 CRD（如 Workflow、Pipeline 等）提供可复用的类型基座。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n1. **共享类型定义** — `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType` 及其常量\n2. **共享枚举常量** — `AuthModeType` 及其常量（`picod`、`none`）\n3. **类型文件组织** — 将共享类型放置在独立的 `shared_types.go`（或类似命名）文件中\n4. **引用迁移** — 确保 AR-001 和 AR-002 的类型文件引用共享类型而非重复定义\n5. **单元测试** — 共享类型常量值验证、零值行为测试\n\n### 不包含\n- 新增 CRD 类型定义\n- CRD YAML 文件生成\n- client-go 代码生成\n- Controller/Reconciler 实现\n\n## 共享类型概要\n\n```\nshared_types.go\n├── ProtocolType (string enum: HTTP | HTTPS)\n│   ├── ProtocolTypeHTTP\n│   └── ProtocolTypeHTTPS\n├── AuthModeType (string enum: picod | none)\n│   ├── AuthModePicoD\n│   └── AuthModeNone\n└── TargetPort (struct)\n    ├── pathPrefix: string (optional)\n    ├── name: string (optional)\n    ├── port: uint32 (required)\n    └── protocol: ProtocolType\n```\n\n## 影响分析\n\n### 直接影响\n| 组件 | 影响 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | 新增 | 共享类型与常量定义文件 |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` | 无变更（引用） | 从共享类型文件引用 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType` |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | 无变更（引用） | 从共享类型文件引用 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`、`AuthModeType` |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | 更新 | 包含 `TargetPort` 的 DeepCopy 方法 |\n\n### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n| 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n|------|----------|\n| 新增 CRD 类型 | 可直接引用共享类型，无需重复定义 |\n| CLI/SDK | 通过共享类型统一端口和协议枚举值 |\n\n## 验收标准\n1. `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n2. `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`、`AuthModeType` 在 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 中有且仅有一份定义\n3. `ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`、`ProtocolTypeHTTPS == \"HTTPS\"`\n4. `AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`、`AuthModeNone == \"none\"`\n5. `TargetPort` 的 DeepCopy 方法在 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 中生成\n6. 单元测试通过\n\n## 状态\n- [ ] 提案审查\n- [ ] 实现\n- [ ] 验证\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775810828456,"end":1775810828465}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775810858700,"sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","part":{"id":"prt_d7692da1c0016EhGV92hV2QMI3","messageID":"msg_d769261560011IBw74KrOV3kpe","sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_3e291aeee2fd4b84a1f22735","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\n`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包中的共享类型与常量是 AgentCube 所有 CRD（AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 及未来新增 CRD）的类型基座。它们定义了跨 CRD 复用的端口配置、协议枚举和认证模式，确保整个 API 层的一致性和可维护性。\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── doc.go                      # 包文档 + k8s 代码生成标记\n        ├── groupversion_info.go        # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder\n        ├── register.go                 # Kind 元数据 + Resource 辅助函数\n        ├── shared_types.go             # 共享类型与常量（本变更核心）\n        ├── shared_types_test.go        # 共享类型测试\n        ├── agent_type.go               # AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义 (AR-001)\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types.go    # CodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义 (AR-002)\n        └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go    # controller-gen object 自动生成\n```\n\n### 1.3 依赖关系\n\n```\n共享类型与常量\n  ├── k8s.io/apimachinery (无外部依赖，纯 Go 类型)\n  │\n  ├──→ AgentRuntime 类型引用 TargetPort、ProtocolType\n  ├──→ CodeInterpreter 类型引用 TargetPort、ProtocolType、AuthModeType\n  └──→ make generate 产出 TargetPort 的 DeepCopy 方法\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. 数据结构\n\n### 2.1 ProtocolType 枚举\n\n```go\n// ProtocolType 定义沙箱端口使用的协议类型\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n```\n\n| 常量 | 值 | 说明 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| `ProtocolTypeHTTP` | `\"HTTP\"` | 超文本传输协议 |\n| `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` | `\"HTTPS\"` | 安全超文本传输协议 |\n\n### 2.2 AuthModeType 枚举\n\n```go\n// AuthModeType 定义沙箱认证模式\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n```\n\n| 常量 | 值 | 说明 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| `AuthModePicoD` | `\"picod\"` | 使用 PicoD 认证 |\n| `AuthModeNone` | `\"none\"` | 无需认证 |\n\n### 2.3 TargetPort 结构体\n\n```go\n// TargetPort 定义沙箱暴露的端口配置\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    Name       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n    Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n```\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | JSON tag | 必填 | 说明 |\n|------|------|----------|------|------|\n| `PathPrefix` | `string` | `pathPrefix,omitempty` | 否 | URL 路径前缀 |\n| `Name` | `string` | `name,omitempty` | 否 | 端口名称 |\n| `Port` | `uint32` | `port` | 是 | 端口号 |\n| `Protocol` | `ProtocolType` | `protocol` | 是 | 协议类型（HTTP/HTTPS） |\n\n---\n\n## 3. 测试策略\n\n### 3.1 常量值测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"HTTP\"), ProtocolTypeHTTP)\n    assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"HTTPS\"), ProtocolTypeHTTPS)\n}\n\nfunc TestAuthModeTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"picod\"), AuthModePicoD)\n    assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"none\"), AuthModeNone)\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 TargetPort 零值行为测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestTargetPortZeroValues(t *testing.T) {\n    tp := TargetPort{Port: 8080}\n    assert.Empty(t, tp.PathPrefix)\n    assert.Empty(t, tp.Name)\n    assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"\"), tp.Protocol)\n}\n```\n\n### 3.3 TargetPort 全字段测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestTargetPortWithAllFields(t *testing.T) {\n    tp := TargetPort{\n        PathPrefix: \"/api\",\n        Name:       \"web\",\n        Port:       8080,\n        Protocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTPS,\n    }\n    assert.Equal(t, \"/api\", tp.PathPrefix)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"web\", tp.Name)\n    assert.Equal(t, uint32(8080), tp.Port)\n    assert.Equal(t, ProtocolTypeHTTPS, tp.Protocol)\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. 实现步骤\n\n### 4.1 文件创建顺序\n\n1. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` — 共享类型与常量定义\n2. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types_test.go` — 共享类型测试\n3. 运行 `make generate` — 更新 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`（包含 TargetPort DeepCopy）\n\n### 4.2 验证检查清单\n\n- [ ] `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n- [ ] `ProtocolType`、`AuthModeType`、`TargetPort` 在包中有且仅有一份定义\n- [ ] 常量值正确：`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`、`AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"` 等\n- [ ] `make generate` 成功更新 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/...` 全部通过\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","time":{"start":1775810858690,"end":1775810858698}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775810881897,"sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","part":{"id":"prt_d76934f0f001cYGzTOmncxSjGU","messageID":"msg_d769261560011IBw74KrOV3kpe","sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_01b1f366ffe141e58783ea2a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine shared types and constants in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` that are reused across AgentRuntime (AR-001) and CodeInterpreter (AR-002) CRD type definitions, establishing a single source of truth for port configuration, protocol enumeration, and authentication mode types.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: ProtocolType enumeration\n\nThe system SHALL define `ProtocolType` as a typed string constant with values `HTTP` and `HTTPS`, serving as the protocol enumeration for sandbox port configuration.\n\n#### Scenario: ProtocolType constants have correct values\n- **GIVEN** the constants `ProtocolTypeHTTP` and `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` are defined\n- **WHEN** their values are inspected\n- **THEN** `ProtocolTypeHTTP` SHALL equal `\"HTTP\"` and `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` SHALL equal `\"HTTPS\"`\n\n#### Scenario: ProtocolType underlying type is string\n- **GIVEN** the `ProtocolType` type definition\n- **WHEN** the underlying type is inspected\n- **THEN** it SHALL be `string`, enabling JSON serialization without custom marshalers\n\n### Requirement: AuthModeType enumeration\n\nThe system SHALL define `AuthModeType` as a typed string constant with values `picod` and `none`, serving as the authentication mode enumeration for sandbox configuration.\n\n#### Scenario: AuthModeType constants have correct values\n- **GIVEN** the constants `AuthModePicoD` and `AuthModeNone` are defined\n- **WHEN** their values are inspected\n- **THEN** `AuthModePicoD` SHALL equal `\"picod\"` and `AuthModeNone` SHALL equal `\"none\"`\n\n#### Scenario: AuthModeType underlying type is string\n- **GIVEN** the `AuthModeType` type definition\n- **WHEN** the underlying type is inspected\n- **THEN** it SHALL be `string`, enabling JSON serialization without custom marshalers\n\n### Requirement: TargetPort struct\n\nThe system SHALL define `TargetPort` as a struct with fields for URL path prefix (`PathPrefix`), port name (`Name`), port number (`Port`), and protocol (`Protocol`), with appropriate JSON tags for Kubernetes CRD serialization.\n\n#### Scenario: TargetPort serializes with correct JSON keys\n- **GIVEN** a `TargetPort` instance with all fields populated\n- **WHEN** the struct is serialized to JSON\n- **THEN** the output SHALL use camelCase keys: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, `protocol`\n\n#### Scenario: TargetPort omits empty optional fields\n- **GIVEN** a `TargetPort` with only `Port` set to `8080`\n- **WHEN** the struct is serialized to JSON\n- **THEN** `pathPrefix`, `name`, and `protocol` SHALL be omitted from the output (omitempty behavior)\n\n#### Scenario: TargetPort Port field is required\n- **GIVEN** a `TargetPort` struct definition\n- **WHEN** the JSON tags are inspected\n- **THEN** `Port` SHALL NOT have `omitempty`, making it a required field in CRD validation\n\n### Requirement: Single source of truth\n\nThe system SHALL define `ProtocolType`, `AuthModeType`, and `TargetPort` exactly once in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`, with both AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter types referencing these shared definitions rather than duplicating them.\n\n#### Scenario: No duplicate type definitions\n- **GIVEN** the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` package\n- **WHEN** the package is compiled\n- **THEN** there SHALL be exactly one definition each of `ProtocolType`, `AuthModeType`, and `TargetPort`\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntime references shared types\n- **GIVEN** the `agent_type.go` file\n- **WHEN** the type definitions are inspected\n- **THEN** `AgentRuntimeSpec` SHALL reference the shared `TargetPort` type for its port configuration\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreter references shared types\n- **GIVEN** the `codeinterpreter_types.go` file\n- **WHEN** the type definitions are inspected\n- **THEN** `CodeInterpreterSpec` SHALL reference the shared `TargetPort` type for its `Ports` field\n\n### Requirement: DeepCopy generation for TargetPort\n\nThe system SHALL generate `DeepCopy` and `DeepCopyInto` methods for `TargetPort` via `controller-gen object`, ensuring safe cross-goroutine value copying.\n\n#### Scenario: DeepCopy methods exist for TargetPort\n- **GIVEN** `make generate` has been run\n- **WHEN** `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` is inspected\n- **THEN** it SHALL contain `DeepCopyInto` and `DeepCopy` methods for `TargetPort`\n\n#### Scenario: DeepCopy produces independent copies\n- **GIVEN** a `TargetPort` with `Name` set to `\"web\"`\n- **WHEN** `DeepCopy()` is called and the copy's `Name` is modified\n- **THEN** the original's `Name` SHALL remain `\"web\"` (no shared references)\n\n### Requirement: Build and test integrity\n\nThe system SHALL compile cleanly and pass all unit tests for the shared types.\n\n#### Scenario: Package compiles\n- **GIVEN** Go toolchain and all dependencies are available\n- **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/apis/...` is executed\n- **THEN** the command SHALL exit with code 0 and produce no errors\n\n#### Scenario: Unit tests pass\n- **GIVEN** the test file `shared_types_test.go` exists\n- **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` is executed\n- **THEN** all tests SHALL pass, including `ProtocolType` constant tests, `AuthModeType` constant tests, and `TargetPort` zero-value/full-field tests\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775810881891,"end":1775810881895}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775810901657,"sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","part":{"id":"prt_d7693a9b200114jdkoHosYX45K","messageID":"msg_d769261560011IBw74KrOV3kpe","sessionID":"ses_2896e27bbffew1TYdtt7sBh7p2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_88e413bee006441bacb2f661","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-003 任务清单\n\n> **Stage**: ST-1 (Proposal)\n> **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n> **Language**: Go\n> **Size**: S\n\n---\n\n## T-001: 创建 shared_types.go — 共享类型与常量定义\n\n- [ ] T-001.01 定义 `type ProtocolType string`\n- [ ] T-001.02 定义常量 `ProtocolTypeHTTP ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"` 和 `ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"`\n- [ ] T-001.03 定义 `type AuthModeType string`\n- [ ] T-001.04 定义常量 `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"` 和 `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n- [ ] T-001.05 定义 `type TargetPort struct`，字段：`PathPrefix string`、`Name string`、`Port uint32`、`Protocol ProtocolType`\n- [ ] T-001.06 所有字段使用正确的 JSON tag（camelCase: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, `protocol`）\n- [ ] T-001.07 `Port` 字段不带 `omitempty`（必填），其余可选字段带 `omitempty`\n\n**验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`；`AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`；`TargetPort` JSON 序列化正确\n\n---\n\n## T-002: 编写单元测试 — 常量值验证\n\n- [ ] T-002.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types_test.go`\n- [ ] T-002.02 测试 `TestProtocolTypeConstants`：验证 `ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`、`ProtocolTypeHTTPS == \"HTTPS\"`\n- [ ] T-002.03 测试 `TestAuthModeTypeConstants`：验证 `AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`、`AuthModeNone == \"none\"`\n\n**验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestProtocolTypeConstants -v` 通过；`-run TestAuthModeTypeConstants -v` 通过\n\n---\n\n## T-003: 编写单元测试 — TargetPort 零值与全字段测试\n\n- [ ] T-003.01 测试 `TestTargetPortZeroValues`：验证仅设置 `Port` 时其他字段为零值\n- [ ] T-003.02 测试 `TestTargetPortWithAllFields`：验证所有字段赋值后正确读取\n\n**验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestTargetPort -v` 通过\n\n---\n\n## T-004: 生成 DeepCopy 方法\n\n- [ ] T-004.01 运行 `make generate`（或 `controller-gen object paths=\"./pkg/apis/...\"`）\n- [ ] T-004.02 验证 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 已更新，包含 `TargetPort` 的 DeepCopy 方法\n- [ ] T-004.03 验证 `git diff --exit-code` 通过（生成文件无意外变更）\n\n**验收**: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 存在且包含 `TargetPort` DeepCopy；`go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n\n---\n\n## T-005: 全量验证门禁\n\n- [ ] T-005.01 `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n- [ ] T-005.02 `go test ./pkg/apis/... -v` 全部通过\n- [ ] T-005.03 `ProtocolType`、`AuthModeType`、`TargetPort` 在包中有且仅有一份定义\n- [ ] T-005.04 `make generate` 成功且 `git diff --exit-code` 通过\n- [ ] T-005.05 常量值正确：`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`、`AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`\n\n**验收**: 全部检查项通过，AR-003 可标记为完成\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775810901649,"end":1775810901655}}}}
